e":"2017-02-13T09:34:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>陳浩天係邊個</blockquote><br />\n大陸嚟嘅？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔識就要大陸黎？<span style=\"color: red;\">大黨我都剩係識出名果堆咋</span>，我坐黃色頭九廣鐵路你都唔知戒奶未呀，話我大陸落黎</blockquote><br />\n話俾人聽自己無知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f894e55ea0aee39d3db285e7bdad95831653a45f","tid":118772,"uid":51121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T09:35:23.000Z","msg":"who fucking care"},{"pid":"e55919b188bdc413b4f2131b36345c9c62906fb0","tid":118772,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T09:40:17.000Z","msg":"其實唔會有國家願意放棄中國咁大舊肥豬肉幫香港， 講到低有邊個國家唔係為自己利益呀， 呢樣嘢好現實<br />\n香港比到咩利益人？"},{"pid":"7fd934d6d4a38a7a5d9db17f5f09283705eaeadb","tid":118772,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T09:41:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>美國生意佬無道德可言<br />\n只有價錢合理，<br />\n老母都可以賣</blockquote><br />\n啱嘅， 你有咩賣比人"},{"pid":"ab4330f247a6ecbb6e3198bc578ce2291d9d814d","tid":118772,"uid":6275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T09:44:07.000Z","msg":"來自黨報嘅認證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"922de7baef0f7f9916c88207c51d882c177cde34","tid":118772,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T09:46:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>陳浩天係邊個</blockquote><br />\n大陸嚟嘅？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔識就要大陸黎？大黨我都剩係識出名果堆咋，我坐黃色頭九廣鐵路你都唔知戒奶未呀，話我大陸落黎</blockquote><br />\n一提起港獨，係香港有邊個唔知道佢大名</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可能我一直在意有議席班人，冇計，政治好殘酷，冇議席影響力好有限</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係香港有議席唔一定對香港本土有好大影響力<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，今後記住兩個人，陳浩天既民族黨，陳雲國師，最花多好一點時間留意一下佢哋。"},{"pid":"11a86b1cdb345933fbdf67d56758650adcf2dcba","tid":118772,"uid":40216,"like":